		<td><b>Branching path gamebooks under free cultural work license</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I plan to release a hypertext reader for NES. It supports branching path <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gamebook" class="postlink">gamebooks</a>  in the style of the <em>Choose Your Own Adventure</em> series. But to demonstrate it, I'll need recommendations of good, free gamebooks to include. (By &quot;free&quot; I mean distributed under terms that grant the <a href="http://freedomdefined.org/Definition" class="postlink">four freedoms of a license for free cultural works</a>, such as Creative Commons Attribution or Attribution-ShareAlike.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


